entries.npc_11: I'm feeling a little light headed, actually.  Perhaps it was all the pesticides...
entries.npc_10: Because.  There is nothing more to be said.  You should feel priveleged to exist in the same galaxy as such a wonderous creature.
entries.npc_5: She is so much more than that.  She is to be praised for her good works at every possible opportunity.
entries.player_9: Why should I care about her?
entries.npc_9: She does whatever needs to be done.  Her grace is an ever flowing fount of knowledge, wisdom, and generosity.
entries.npc_8: Perhaps you should ask around about her.  She is quite powerful here on Tatooine.
entries.player_7: I think that's what I just said.
entries.npc_4: You've never heard of her eminence the Lady Valarian?
entries.npc_7: Gardening is noble pursuit no matter where it is performed.
entries.player_4: Must not be much work on Tatooine.
entries.npc_6: My gloves didn't give it away?
entries.npc_1: Madam's not here, but what can I help you with?
